	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I've written some code for NES using MMC1 and SNES still scares me.  A game like Mega Man X3, Yoshi's Island and Starfox which all have co-processors must have software for three CPUs with radically different opcodes and addressing modes.  Any other platform like that?

		

